WEBVTT

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:16.640 line:20%
Piyush, cek pasti ada
mangga di pasaran sekarang.

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:18.720 line:20%
Rukmini menyukai 'Aamras'..

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:20.440 line:20%
Jadi, belilah dua kilogram.

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:22.800 line:20%
Aku akan melakukannya
meskipun kamu tidak memberitahuku.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:23.960 line:20%
Anda tidak memiliki kesabaran

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:25.920 line:20%
datang ke pasar
meskipun Anda sakit.

